[As already noted in a comment made by Mod.AS, FMDV-O has been reported in China since November 2014. See posting 20161124.4653143.

To date, 4 outbreaks have been reported associated with the November 2014 event. The provinces where FMDV-O has been identified are Jiangsu, Sichuan, Guizhou y Jiangxi. See event summary and updated map at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?reportid=16587. - Mod.CRD

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4666050,358.]
